    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my car and it has been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been looked after with a lot of care. You\u2019ll find it runs smoothly and still has that great curb appeal! It\u2019s perfect for anyone looking for a dependable, high-quality ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve truly loved driving this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Drop me a message if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
