    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and an M-Variable Lock limited-slip differential for optimal power distribution. The chassis is mechanically sound, benefiting from essential subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushings for sharpened turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic wear typical of a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are robust, with recent valve adjustments and a cooling system overhaul ensuring thermal efficiency under load.",
      "price": 34500.0,
