    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2019 BMW X5 xDrive40i that has been thoughtfully maintained and is ready for its next owner. The Alpine White exterior remains vibrant and holds a high-gloss finish, with only minor, unavoidable stone chips on the lower front valance. The wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with roughly 70% tread remaining. Inside, the Canberra Beige leather interior is in excellent shape; the seats are firm, the bolsters show minimal wear, and the cabin is entirely smoke-free. All premium features, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and the dual 12.3-inch display screens, are fully functional with no electronic glitches. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a comprehensive maintenance log available. We recently completed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection, confirming that the brakes and suspension are in solid working order. The 3.0L turbocharged engine runs smoothly and the 8-speed transmission shifts imperceptibly. This car offers a refined driving experience without the 'new car' price tag. Includes two key fobs and all-weather floor mats.",
      "price": 31500.0,
