      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained executive vehicle, which stands as a testament to disciplined ownership and engineering excellence. Having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this unit remains in commendable mechanical and aesthetic order, ensuring a refined and dependable driving experience. It represents an exceptional acquisition for the discerning professional seeking the ideal intersection of sophisticated performance and lasting value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
