    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable, smooth ride without any of the stress. It's clean, runs beautifully, and is just waiting for a new owner to take it on some fresh adventures! I'd love for you to come by, check it out, and see how great it feels behind the wheel. Let's get you on the road!",
      "price": 33500.0,
