    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and metallic rasp. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously sorted: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension maintains excellent damping characteristics with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback and neutral handling balance this platform is known for. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a pure analog performance experience.",
